se%2Fbig5%2Fnonmarxists%2Fmao%2F19420208.htm&d=bTkwEGnHH2OXdpYsGZaakuBrFmK%2FfjgW9YhWFGnkYF4%3D&h=d8630c9c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.marxists.org/chinese/big5/nonmarxists/mao/19420208.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n拋磚引玉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T05:04:45.000Z","msg":"「許多國家都掛起了共和國的招牌，實際上卻是一點民主也沒有。」<br />\n〈論新民主主義的憲政〉，1940年2月20日<br />\n<br />\n「他們口裡的憲政，不過是『掛羊頭賣狗肉』。他們是在掛憲政的羊頭，賣一黨專政的狗肉。我並不是隨便罵他們，我的話是有根據的，這根據就在於他們一面談憲政，一面卻不給人民以絲毫的自由。」<br />\n〈論新民主主義的憲政〉，1940年2月20日<br />\n<br />\n習總<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T05:08:09.000Z","msg":"一國兩制<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n基本法是小憲法<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e41276448283cb5cd8afc8083d023c51e59c1721","tid":1328830,"uid":126889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T05:10:42.000Z","msg":"你冇野講"},{"pid":"3311c7c2b3a6edc3f7ae502b2d2db82cb3de2d57","tid":1328830,"uid":126889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T05:17:19.000Z","msg":"我無講野"},{"pid":"410e634d72279536bc0e01421508d2813e1e654b","tid":1328830,"uid":126889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T05:23:22.000Z","msg":"我冇講野"},{"pid":"5f36604cb11f55ac56bb125e7c9bc1f79e72aab1","tid":1328830,"uid":137506,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T05:24:26.000Z","msg":"毛魔玩抗爭運動真係一流<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ea27da053cc7b83f19ef3990108063c364ca1ee","tid":1328830,"uid":126889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T05:26:49.000